      "message": "spelling fixed.\n\nphrasing: I want to emphasize that this is mostly due to transient errors from network or Gerrit and that this is unlikely to hide true permanent (aka SUBMIT_FAILURE) error. Hence, I find \"possibly transient\" not as good. WDYT?",
