      "message": "Since these names are within a SubmitStatus enum within GerritChange, I think that the SUBMIT part of the name is redundant -- the names could also be:\n\n SUBMIT_STATUS_UNSPECIFIED (submit never tried)\n UNKNOWN\n FAILURE\n SCUCESS\n\nwhat do you think?\n\nAnother possibility, is that we could add a NOT_TRIED value, and then we would never (intentionally) send a  UNSPECIFIED value.",
